In the misty mountains there was once a peacful town called LeTown.
Where people lived in harmony, shielded from evil.

#Second 
But one day, the evil from deep within the caves woke up,
The monsters started to move further down the slopes

#third
By the second day they spotted LeTown.
They began plundering a steeling from the habitants.
Setting houses on fire

#fourth
When the people of LeTown thought the nightmare was over something
terrible happened. The monsters broke into the castle and took the princess
and brought here with them back to their caves

#fifth
The future of LeTown is depending on one man.
His mission is to hunt down the monsters and rescue
the princess. 

#last
Welcome to Le Quest!